1
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:49,760
Sis Fei

2
00:00:51,080 --> 00:00:52,320
It's hard to guard against an inside thief.

3
00:00:53,920 --> 00:00:55,160
If we can help you

4
00:00:55,360 --> 00:00:56,600
catch this inside thief,

5
00:00:57,400 --> 00:00:59,360
could you spare the two of us?

6
00:01:00,120 --> 00:01:01,840
You're saying I've got a thief here?

7
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:10,200
Kun.

8
00:01:12,400 --> 00:01:13,360
You betrayed me.

9
00:01:16,960 --> 00:01:17,920
You're getting back at me, huh?

10
00:01:18,680 --> 00:01:20,880
Sis, you know we've had bad blood.

11
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,160
I've risked my life for you for years.

12
00:01:23,160 --> 00:01:24,360
Fought so many hard battles with Hong Ye.

13
00:01:24,360 --> 00:01:25,680
How could I betray you?

14
00:01:26,080 --> 00:01:27,400
Don't use your new identity

15
00:01:27,440 --> 00:01:28,200
to test me.

16
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:30,240
Then this video...

17
00:01:30,720 --> 00:01:31,720
who shot it?

18
00:01:33,720 --> 00:01:35,040
So I'm stuck taking the fall, huh?

19
00:01:35,320 --> 00:01:36,800
Who shot this damn video?

20
00:01:37,360 --> 00:01:38,160
I did.

21
00:01:38,480 --> 00:01:39,520
How could I have shot it?

22
00:01:39,520 --> 00:01:41,400
How can you prove I shot it?

23
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:54,200
Sis Fei.

24
00:01:56,160 --> 00:01:56,680
The evidence.

25
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:57,920
Here, take it.

26
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:01,840
If I'm not mistaken,

27
00:02:02,240 --> 00:02:03,280
on his phone,

28
00:02:03,440 --> 00:02:04,640
there should be a control system.

29
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:07,640
Take out your phone.

30
00:02:08,200 --> 00:02:08,720
Sis...

31
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:09,480
I messed up.

32
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:10,800
I was forced.

33
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:12,600
Hong Ye forced me, Sis!

34
00:02:12,720 --> 00:02:13,760
People who betray me

35
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:14,880
don't get to make excuses.

36
00:02:15,040 --> 00:02:15,680
Sis...

37
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:17,200
I messed up, Sis!

38
00:02:17,600 --> 00:02:18,400
Sis Fei.

39
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:19,360
Killing him right now

40
00:02:19,880 --> 00:02:20,760
does you no good at all.

41
00:02:21,480 --> 00:02:22,480
Anyone who betrays me

42
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:23,960
has to die.

43
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:26,360
You've got leverage on his family.

44
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:28,520
You can still make him

45
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:30,000
work for you.

46
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:31,720
Sis...

47
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:32,800
Sis!

48
00:02:32,920 --> 00:02:33,800
Sis, Sis!

49
00:02:34,720 --> 00:02:35,520
I'm begging you.

50
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:38,200
Text Hong Ye.

51
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:40,680
Say the deal with President Shen

52
00:02:41,040 --> 00:02:41,960
fell through.

53
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:44,560
I'll text him.

54
00:02:44,600 --> 00:02:46,000
I'll text him!

55
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:52,040
It's sent.

56
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:52,800
It's sent.

57
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:58,280
Do it yourself.

58
00:03:14,920 --> 00:03:15,520
Uncle.

59
00:03:16,120 --> 00:03:17,120
Brother Kun just messaged.

60
00:03:17,720 --> 00:03:18,600
The talks broke down.

61
00:03:19,480 --> 00:03:21,400
Sis Fei even wants to poach our people.

62
00:03:21,400 --> 00:03:22,960
In her dreams.

63
00:03:24,480 --> 00:03:25,320
Why do I feel like

64
00:03:25,480 --> 00:03:27,280
they sent it to us on purpose?

65
00:03:27,880 --> 00:03:28,680
What do you mean?

66
00:03:29,040 --> 00:03:30,240
They found out about Brother Kun.

67
00:03:31,520 --> 00:03:33,600
This Feifei is ruthless,

68
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:35,600
but she's never been that sharp.

69
00:03:36,200 --> 00:03:37,880
She probably didn't notice anything.

70
00:03:38,480 --> 00:03:40,080
But this Zhao Wudi...

71
00:03:40,760 --> 00:03:42,360
that's a different story.

72
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:44,920
So what do we do?

73
00:03:45,200 --> 00:03:46,480
We planted people by her side,

74
00:03:46,480 --> 00:03:47,680
and Kun's not the only one.

75
00:03:48,760 --> 00:03:49,560
What're you panicking for?

76
00:03:58,160 --> 00:03:59,000
Feeling sorry for her?

77
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:01,200
She made such a huge mistake,

78
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:04,160
dragging you into that deadly jungle.

79
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:05,560
She deserves to be punished.

80
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:07,840
So you still care about me.

81
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:12,000
Caring about your own wife,

82
00:04:13,720 --> 00:04:14,520
isn't that only natural?

83
00:04:16,080 --> 00:04:16,880
Forget it.

84
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:18,720
I wasn't going to hold it against her anyway.

85
00:04:22,320 --> 00:04:23,800
Right now, the priority

86
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:25,360
is the deal with Hong Ye the day after tomorrow.

87
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:27,720
Let's hope that batch of fake chips

88
00:04:27,960 --> 00:04:29,120
doesn't have any slip-ups.

89
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:33,200
I've already checked them.

90
00:04:33,520 --> 00:04:34,520
No problems.

91
00:04:34,760 --> 00:04:36,240
They should arrive tomorrow.

92
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:39,560
What's wrong?

93
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:45,720
I'm fine.

94
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:48,280
Probably haven't been sleeping enough lately.

95
00:04:48,280 --> 00:04:49,280
I've got a bit of a cold.

96
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:50,960
I'm gonna go lie down.

97
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:52,800
A Di.

98
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:16,480
I just don't get it.

99
00:05:16,520 --> 00:05:18,680
If you just sleep with Sis Xingyu once,

100
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:20,200
it would cure your poison.

101
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:22,240
Why make it so complicated?

102
00:05:23,320 --> 00:05:24,840
She still doesn't know I'm Zhao Wudi.

103
00:05:26,520 --> 00:05:27,640
Besides,

104
00:05:27,760 --> 00:05:29,080
if I do it like that,

105
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:30,600
it's disrespectful to her.

106
00:05:32,760 --> 00:05:34,320
Only if I'm the fake Zhao Wudi

107
00:05:35,280 --> 00:05:36,760
can she be safe.

108
00:05:37,400 --> 00:05:39,640
So you'll keep hiding it from Sis Xingyu,

109
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:41,000
and keep faking amnesia.

110
00:05:41,880 --> 00:05:43,880
You're one stubborn, infuriating man.

111
00:05:44,280 --> 00:05:45,080
Whatever.

112
00:05:45,640 --> 00:05:46,800
I'll help you out.

113
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:02,240
Youyou, what did you do?

114
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:03,960
Guess.

115
00:07:15,080 --> 00:07:15,640
Bro.

116
00:07:16,280 --> 00:07:17,280
You're finally here.

117
00:07:21,440 --> 00:07:22,200
Sorry.

118
00:07:22,400 --> 00:07:23,280
I got here late.

119
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:24,640
Have a seat.

120
00:07:29,880 --> 00:07:31,480
That A Di you wanted me to look into,

121
00:07:31,960 --> 00:07:32,720
I got the info.

122
00:07:33,240 --> 00:07:34,440
No need.

123
00:07:34,760 --> 00:07:36,080
I think he is Zhao Wudi.

124
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:37,520
We

125
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:39,560
have to help him get his real memories back.

126
00:07:45,440 --> 00:07:46,680
His name is Ren Feifan.

127
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:49,680
He's the killer who murdered Wudi.

128
00:07:51,760 --> 00:07:52,960
He didn't just kill him,

129
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:54,280
he stole his face too.

130
00:07:55,280 --> 00:07:56,960
I've already compared the DNA

131
00:07:56,960 --> 00:07:58,360
and their physical traits.

132
00:07:58,840 --> 00:07:59,880
I'm sure it's him.

133
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:03,640
This pager,

134
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:04,720
you should've seen it before.

135
00:08:05,360 --> 00:08:06,360
Wudi never had one.

136
00:08:16,880 --> 00:08:18,080
Is that true?

137
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:21,760
You're not Zhao Wudi at all.

138
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:24,480
You're just the man who killed him,

139
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:26,360
and stole his identity.

140
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:27,800
No.

141
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:29,800
I can't tell her.

142
00:08:32,240 --> 00:08:33,040
Xingyu.

143
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:34,600
I really have amnesia.

144
00:08:34,920 --> 00:08:36,240
All I remember is waking up,

145
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:37,240
in Dongba.

146
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:38,320
I only remember

147
00:08:38,640 --> 00:08:39,640
my name is A Di.

148
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:40,840
That's all I remember.

149
00:08:41,160 --> 00:08:42,480
Don't buy his bullshit.

150
00:08:42,680 --> 00:08:43,840
Maybe this punk's amnesia

151
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:44,640
is all just an act.

152
00:08:45,160 --> 00:08:46,440
He killed my brother,

153
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:48,640
and used his face to fool my sister.

154
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:50,320
Say the word.

155
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,880
I'll kill him for you right now.

156
00:08:51,880 --> 00:08:53,040
Enough.

157
00:08:57,520 --> 00:08:58,240
A Di.

158
00:09:00,400 --> 00:09:01,600
Or whoever you are...

159
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:03,280
Right now, I don't believe

160
00:09:03,280 --> 00:09:05,320
either of your one-sided stories.

161
00:09:05,960 --> 00:09:07,360
I'll help you get your memory back.

162
00:09:08,720 --> 00:09:09,680
Your real memories.

163
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:12,680
When the truth comes out,

164
00:09:13,760 --> 00:09:15,120
if at that time

165
00:09:16,160 --> 00:09:18,480
I find out you really killed Zhao Wudi,

166
00:09:20,520 --> 00:09:22,160
I'll kill you with my own hands.

167
00:09:24,680 --> 00:09:25,480
Fine.

168
00:09:29,160 --> 00:09:30,680
But right now, what matters most is

169
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:32,480
the deal with Hong Ye the day after tomorrow.

170
00:09:32,760 --> 00:09:34,160
We have to rescue Dr. Zhang.

171
00:09:35,560 --> 00:09:36,440
The chips,

172
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:37,400
and the plan,

173
00:09:38,040 --> 00:09:38,880
are they all ready?

174
00:09:40,720 --> 00:09:42,120
The fake chips are ready.

175
00:09:43,240 --> 00:09:43,960
Now we're just waiting for the day after tomorrow.

176
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:57,440
Shen Xingchen.

177
00:09:58,280 --> 00:10:00,040
What the hell are you after?

178
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:03,720
There's still a lot

179
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:06,240
I haven't remembered yet.

180
00:10:07,680 --> 00:10:08,320
Who's there?

181
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:22,640
Don't waste your energy.

182
00:10:23,720 --> 00:10:25,280
You can't do anything.

183
00:10:26,160 --> 00:10:28,200
You're a useless piece of trash now.

184
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:30,280
I could crush you

185
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:33,600
as easily as crushing an ant.

186
00:10:37,080 --> 00:10:37,880
Who are you?

187
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:39,240
Who am I?

188
00:10:43,520 --> 00:10:45,600
Of course you don't know who I am.

189
00:10:46,360 --> 00:10:48,520
Everyone who's ever seen me

190
00:10:49,120 --> 00:10:50,120
is dead.

191
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:51,360
Except for Zhao Wudi.

192
00:10:54,040 --> 00:10:55,040
But he...

193
00:10:55,800 --> 00:10:57,880
was killed by you too.

194
00:11:00,320 --> 00:11:01,480
I didn't kill Zhao Wudi.

195
00:11:01,800 --> 00:11:02,720
I didn't kill him.

196
00:11:03,040 --> 00:11:03,520
No.

197
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:04,880
I really am Zhao Wudi.

198
00:11:05,280 --> 00:11:06,160
You?

199
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:08,080
You're nothing but

200
00:11:08,080 --> 00:11:10,160
someone wearing his face.

201
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:11,920
You're just a

202
00:11:12,160 --> 00:11:15,720
pathetic worm who doesn't know who he is.

203
00:11:16,360 --> 00:11:17,440
I really am Zhao Wudi.

204
00:11:17,440 --> 00:11:18,600
I just lost my memory.

205
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:21,000
Don't try to trick me with that.

206
00:11:21,400 --> 00:11:22,120
Break!
